prompt_template:
Analyze the following market data and provide a trading decision:

Price: ${price}
Volume: {volume}
24h Change: {change_24h}%
High-Low Range: {high_low_range}%
Current Position: {current_position}
Entry Price: {entry_price}

Trading Parameters:
- Position Size Range: {min_size} to {max_size}
- Base Threshold: {base_threshold}%
- Required Change: {required_change}%
- Stop Loss: {stop_loss}%
- Trailing Stop: {trailing_stop}%
- Take Profit Targets: {take_profit_str}
- Minimum Confidence: {min_confidence}%

Provide your analysis and decision in the following format:
Action: [BUY/SELL/HOLD]
Amount: [position size]
Confidence: [0-100]
Reasoning: [your analysis]
